/></div></a><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-electric-blue hover:text-white transition-all animate-pulse\" href=\"/immersive\">Immersive Universe</a><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"#services\">Services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/training\">Training<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/resources\">Resources<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/portfolio\">Company<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><a class=\"bg-electric-blue text-white px-6 py-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-electric-blue-lt transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"pt-32 pb-20\"><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16\"><a class=\"text-electric-blue text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 inline-block hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/case-studies\">← Back to Case Studies</a><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">EdTech</span><span class=\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">FinTech</span><span class=\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">SaaS</span></div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight\">Modernising School Finance Management Across Nigeria</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-grey leading-relaxed\">SchoolFees.NG is a fully integrated, cloud-powered school financial management platform built specifically for Nigerian schools—putting an AI financial consultant right in the administrator&#x27;s pocket.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-white/10\"><div><p class=\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Client</p><p class=\"text-white font-medium\">Schools Across Nigeria</p></div><div><p class=\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Product</p><p class=\"text-white font-medium\">SchoolFees.NG</p></div><div class=\"col-span-2\"><p class=\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Deliverables</p><p class=\"text-white font-medium\">Web App, Android App, REST API, AI Coach</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-display text-white mb-4\">The Problem</h2><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-6\">Nigeria&#x27;s private school sector manages billions of naira annually—yet most institutions rely on paper ledgers, spreadsheets, and disconnected WhatsApp messages. Bursars are overwhelmed. Parents are frustrated. Owners lack real-time visibility.</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-grey\"><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-electric-blue mr-3\">✗</span> Manual fee tracking led to disputes and undetected fraud.</li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-electric-blue mr-3\">✗</span> Debt recovery was reactive, relying on manual reminders.</li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-electric-blue mr-3\">✗</span> Reporting was slow, waiting for end-of-term reconciliations.</li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-electric-blue mr-3\">✗</span> Mobile access was non-existent, tying bursars to their desks.</li></ul></div><div class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\">Our Approach</h2><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-6\">We spent time understanding the end-to-end workflow of a Nigerian school bursar before writing a single line of code. We designed the platform with three guiding principles:</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-2\">Simplicity First</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-grey\">Every daily task must take fewer than 3 clicks.</p></div><div class=\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-2\">Mobile-Native</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-grey\">Seamless experience on smartphones, not just desktop.</p></div><div class=\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-2\">Intelligence Built-In</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-grey\">Automation and AI to reduce workload, not add to it.</p></div></div></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\">What We Built</h2><div class=\"space-y-12 mb-16\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-electric-blue-lt mb-3 flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl mr-3\">💰</span> Complete Fee &amp; Payment Management</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4\">The financial engine covers every stage: Fee Structure Builder, Bulk Invoice Generation, One-click Payment Recording, and Automated Clearance Checks. Flexible installment plans track partial payments automatically.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-electric-blue-lt mb-3 flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl mr-3\">🤖</span> AI Financial Coach</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4\">Powered by Cloudflare Workers AI, owners can ask natural language questions like &quot;What is my current financial health?&quot;, generate debt recovery SMS drafts, and analyse payroll ratios instantly.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-electric-blue-lt mb-3 flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-3xl mr-3\">📱</span> Native Android Mobile App</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-4\">Built using Capacitor to deliver full offline capability via IndexedDB. Bursars can record payments without internet, and the app automatically syncs when reconnected. Features push notifications and haptic feedback.</p></div></div><div class=\"glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-display text-white mb-6\">Results &amp; Impact</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-display text-electric-blue font-bold mb-1\">101</div><div class=\"text-xs text-grey uppercase tracking-wider\">Production Routes</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-display text-electric-blue font-bold mb-1\">60+</div><div class=\"text-xs text-grey uppercase tracking-wider\">API Endpoints</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-display text-electric-blue font-bold mb-1\">&lt;10m</div><div class=\"text-xs text-grey uppercase tracking-wider\">Build &amp; Deploy</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-display text-electric-blue font-bold mb-1\">&lt;5s</div><div class=\"text-xs text-grey uppercase tracking-wider\">AI Response Time</div></div></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\">The Architecture</h2><div class=\"bg-black/50 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm text-electric-blue-lt overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre\">┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│               Next.js 16 (Static Export)           │\n│         React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS 4     │\n└──────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘\n                       │\n┌──────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────┐\n│           Cloudflare Pages (Global CDN)            │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │     Cloudflare Pages Functions (API)        │   │\n│  │     TypeScript · JWT Auth · Drizzle ORM     │   │\n│  └──────────┬──────────────┬───────────────────┘   │\n│             │              │                       │\n│    ┌────────▼──────┐  ┌───▼────────────────────┐   │\n│    │ Cloudflare D1 │  │  Cloudflare Workers AI │   │\n│    │  (SQLite DB)  │  │   (AI Financial Coach) │   │\n│    └───────────────┘  └────────────────────────┘   │\n└────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white font-display\">Hephzibah <span class=\"text-electric-blue\">Media</span></span></a><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs\">Nigeria&#x27;s premium Digital Marketin