 Parents are frustrated. Owners lack real-time visibility.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3 text-grey\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"✗\"}],\" Manual fee tracking led to disputes and undetected fraud.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"✗\"}],\" Debt recovery was reactive, relying on manual reminders.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"✗\"}],\" Reporting was slow, waiting for end-of-term reconciliations.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"✗\"}],\" Mobile access was non-existent, tying bursars to their desks.\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\",\"children\":\"Our Approach\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-6\",\"children\":\"We spent time understanding the end-to-end workflow of a Nigerian school bursar before writing a single line of code. We designed the platform with three guiding principles:\"}],\"$L15\"]}],\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\"]}]]}],null,\"$L1a\"]}]\n1b:[]\n12:\"$W1b\"\n13:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{\"children\":\"$L1d\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1e\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$1f\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.Metadata\",\"children\":\"$L20\"}]}]}],null]}]\n21:I[484,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n15:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-mi